title: For Sale:  M91 1918 Remington made Mosin Nagant
postcontent: M91 1918 Remington made Mosin Nagant. This rifle was sporterized a very long time ago and looks very similar to a Bannerman conversion, although I don’t believe it is. I have not fired this rifle, got it in trade a few months back but previous owner stated it fired fine. Nothing on this rifle is numbers matching, but it is complete and cycles well. Barrel has strong rifling, but it is also evident that there has been corrosion in the past...possibly put away dirty for several decades…IDK.
